<h1>Bohemienne</h1>


<div id="articleBodyTop">

<div id="articleBodyImageH">
<span id="articleImageH"></span>
<img src="http://cache.boston.com/resize/bonzai-fba/Globe_Photo/2008/08/25/1219707991_4333/539w.jpg" title="" height="504" width="539" alt="" border="0" />

(b&amp;#233;atrice peltre for the boston globe)
</div></div>


<div class="utility">
    <span id="byline">
        
        
        
    </span>
    <div class="cf"></div>
    <span id="dateline">
          
          
          August 27, 2008
    </span>
    <div class="cf"></div>
